Description: bc-* ecosystem concurrency primitives (development files)
 MPMC queue-backed worker pool with configurable worker count,
 typed dispatch, shared cross-worker context, and signal-safe
 shutdown coordination.
 .
 This package ships the static library, public headers, and
 pkg-config descriptor required to build against bc-concurrency.
